<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
<meta content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=no" id="viewport" name="viewport">
<title>商户-投票功能</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/reset.css"/>
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/style.css"/>
<script src="js/zepto.js" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>
<script src="js/js.js" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>
</head>

<body>
<header> 
	<i class="left" id="icon_goback"></i>
    <div class="title">投票功能</div>
    <i class="right"><a href="#">+发布投票</a></i> 
</header>

<section>
	<script>
		$(function(){
			$(".sh_prompt_infor_closs").click(function(){
				$(".sh_prompt_infor_box").hide();
			});
		});
    </script>
	<div class="sh_prompt_infor_box">
    	<p>新添加的投票要启用之后才能显示在前台！</p>
        <div class="sh_prompt_infor_closs"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="sh_search_box">
        <div class="sh_search_int"> <span>投票标题</span>
            <input type="text" value="">
            <input type="button" class="btn" value="搜索">
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="sh_coupon_tab_box">
    	<div class="sh_list_public_box">
            <ul>
                <li class="list_box mb10" style="border-top:1px solid #dedede;">
                    <div>
                        <div class="sh_coupon_nr">
                            <div class="wz">
                            	<p><span class="black3 mr20">我发起的活动的活动咋样</span>未启用</p>
                                <p><span class="mr20">结束时间：2015-08-07</span>5人投票</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="sh_vote_nr">
                        	<div class="fl">
                            	<p>投票banner</p>
                            	<img src="img/vote_banner.jpg" width="109" height="50">
                            </div>
                            <div class="fl">
                            	<p>二维码</p>
                            	<img src="img/weixin_img.jpg" width="50" height="50">
                            </div>
                            <div class="fl">
                            	<p>投票结果</p>
                            	<img src="img/weixin_img.jpg" width="50" height="50">
                            </div>
                            <div class="clear"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="sh_buy_date bg1">
                        	<p>http://www.baocms.cn/mobile/vote/index/vote_id/17.html</p> 
                        </div>
                        <div class="btn_box"><a class="btn" href="#">编辑</a><a class="btn" href="#">启用投票</a><a class="btn" href="#">设置选项</a><a class="btn" href="#">查看结果</a></div>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="list_box mb10" style="border-top:1px solid #dedede;">
                    <div>
                        <div class="sh_coupon_nr">
                            <div class="wz">
                            	<p><span class="black3 mr20">我发起的活动的活动咋样</span>未启用</p>
                                <p><span class="mr20">结束时间：2015-08-07</span>5人投票</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="sh_vote_nr">
                        	<div class="fl">
                            	<p>投票banner</p>
                            	<img src="img/vote_banner.jpg" width="109" height="50">
                            </div>
                            <div class="fl">
                            	<p>二维码</p>
                            	<img src="img/weixin_img.jpg" width="50" height="50">
                            </div>
                            <div class="fl">
                            	<p>投票结果</p>
                            	<img src="img/weixin_img.jpg" width="50" height="50">
                            </div>
                            <div class="clear"></div>
